*Mislili* smo da će biti lakše nego što je bilo u stvarnosti. (We thought it would be easier than it was in reality.)

*Mislili* smo da će sve biti drugačije. (We thought everything would be different.)

Oni su se *mislili* da će uspeti. (They thought they would succeed.)

*Mislili* su da će se sve promeniti. (They thought everything would change.)

Oni nisu *mislili* da zavisi od njih. (They didn't think it depended on them.)

*Mislili* smo da će to biti nemoguće. (We thought it would be impossible.)